name: Queer Beetle
description: Respect for all bodies and love. Queer beetles is not just a metaphor, but a reality: in some species of beetles it has been observed the coupling between individuals of the same sex. If your hatred is "based on nature": know that it's invalidated by it, find another way to nutre your ugly mind. I'm a brazilian woman artist, you can find me at twitter/instagram by @ocvvvlta!
